http://www.savers.org:80/nationalreview/daily/nr112196.html 204.71.237.73 19970108084050 text/html 3180
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:41:07 GMT
