<H3><I><FONT SIZE = "+2">P</FONT>urpose</I></H3>
<P>
The purpose of the Heritage Job Bank is to try to match conservative job seekers with government/public policy-related positions.  Due to the volume, we do not conduct interviews and can not take any phone calls.  The recommendations you use are important so please list people who can speak to both your professional qualifications and your conservative ideology. For more information contact <a href="mailto: jobbank@heritage.org">Krissy Ganong</a> at (202) 546-4400. 

