http://www.savers.org:80/discovery/gingrich.html 204.71.237.73 19970108084840 text/html 11252
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:48:56 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:31:08 GMT
