Fairfax, VA             Media General                   43
Minocqua, WI            W02CF                           2 
Niagara, WI             Niagara TV Co-op                33
Rice Lake, WI           Marcus Cable                    96
Sheboygan, WI           Marcus Cable                    20
Tigerton, WI            WCW TV 4                        4 
Tomah, WI               Marcus Cable                    6 
Cheyenne, WY            K39DQ                           39
Laramie, WY             K63EZ                           63
</pre></center>



<p><font size=+1>
If you have a satellite dish, NET is available on Galaxy 6, 
Transponder 7.
<p>
If your cable company does not carry NET, you can obtain a postcard 
to mail to your local cable operator requesting the network by 
calling 1-800-225-4008. When calling, make sure to mention that you 
saw this on our web site!

</font>
</body>
</html>
